<p>I'm trying to make script, that works like step by step slider with a period of clicks. The main goal was to make LABEL be the trigger of that clicks. I made the script, but how to make it work with loop: when it reaches the last LABEL it goes to first in cycle? Any help?  <a href="http://codepen.io/NeedHate/pen/ojBmXM" rel="nofollow">http://codepen.io/NeedHate/pen/ojBmXM</a></p>  <pre><code>$('label').each(function(i, e) {   var delay = 1000;   setTimeout(function() {     $('label').removeClass('button-checked');     $(e).trigger("click").addClass('button-checked');    }, i * delay); }); </code></pre>